    "Another example is the SCONE platform (Scontain 2023) to build and run secure applications with the help of Intel SGX.",
    "TEE can be divided into hardware and software environments.",
    "Secure Execution Environment (SEE) is a related concept to TEE, which mainly highlights security measures to safeguard the execution environment, such as access control, encryption, isolation, and integrity checks (Mo et al. 2021).",
